      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. i've heard some parents saying the school is basically just pushing a specific agenda and that we shouldn't be teaching this stuff to kids who are too young to process it. on the other hand, i also hear people saying that if we don't teach it, we're basically being hateful or something. i'm just trying to figure out if there's actually a valid middle ground here or if one side is just objectively right about what's best for kids.",
